videos.description: Auburn Tigers defeat Alabama Crimson Tide 100-81, with outstanding performances from Walker Kessler who had 14 points and 12 rebounds, and Wendell Green Jr. who had 23 points.

videos.description: After a 100-81 thrashing of rival Alabama, Walker Kessler and Bruce Pearl dish on what makes Auburn so special this year.
videos.headline: Pearl says No. 1 Tigers 'have been righteous all year'
